(44, 19, 20, 53, 3, 1, 1, 'the word of God', 'Growth of the Word', 'This connection highlights the theme of the word of God gaining influence and being glorified. Both passages emphasize the power and spread of the word, suggesting its effectiveness in different contexts.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 19, 21, 44, 20, 22, 22, 'I must also see Rome', 'Paul''s Journey to Jerusalem', 'Both passages emphasize Paul''s intention to go to Jerusalem. The phrase ''bound in the spirit'' in Acts 20:22 connects to his earlier purpose in Acts 19:21, highlighting his commitment to this journey.', 'theme', 0.349, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
