(44, 19, 21, 45, 1, 13, 13, 'purposed in the spirit', 'Paul''s Intent to Visit', 'This connection highlights Paul''s intention to visit different regions, including Rome. Both passages emphasize his purpose in traveling to spread the gospel among the Gentiles.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
